        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer100908490" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12053198413447969903">Interesting plot, good characters, but no sex. Yeah, I know, I&apos;m shallow.</span>
  <span id="freeText12053198413447969903" style="display:none">Interesting plot, good characters, but no sex. Yeah, I know, I'm shallow.</span>
