        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1928026943" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6423675993739333828">3.5 stars. M/M. A nice story about a victim of a brutal gay bashing (his partner was killed) and a psychiatrist who moves into another room at the boarding house where the victim (and several others) live. The victim is completely closed off, haunted by his memories and injuries. The psychiatrist tries to help him open up. Good idea, but the book moved slowly for me. I was tempted to give up a few times, but happy I finished.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


