<li class='cover' id='bookCover_9564239'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/9564239-rescue-me"><img alt="Rescue Me" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1287877837l/9564239._SX98_.jpg" />
