<span id="freeTextContainer13150950272324969497">Dawn lives in Huntington, West Virginia, and graduated from the W. Page Pitt School of Journalism &amp; Mass Communications at Marshall University. An avid reader and storyteller since childhood, she was first published by Dreamspinner Press in 2009, shortly after discovering a delightful appetite for gay romantic fiction. Her interests include writing, seeking full civil rights for the LGBTQ communit</span>
